Former Big Brother Naija housemate, Pere Egbi, has reacted to reports that the reality TV show season 7 form is for sale. According to the BBN star, no one should ask how much the form cost as it is free He wrote, “Please BBNaija Auditions are free. No come dey ask me how much to buy form.” -Advertisement- Recall that on Sunday, the organizers of the show officially announced the season 7 audition, urging interested participants to submit a 3-minute video for the audition via their website.